{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.019.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">R\u00e9volte de Sch\u00e9ba, Benjamite. \u2014 Rentr\u00e9e de David dans J\u00e9rusalem. \u2014 Amasa, ancien chef de l\u2019arm\u00e9e d\u2019Absalom, tu\u00e9 par Joab<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-13: cf. (2 S 19:41-43. Pr 17:14.) (2 S 19:13; 3:23-30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Il se trouvait l\u00e0 un m\u00e9chant homme, nomm\u00e9 Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri, Benjamite. Il sonna de la trompette, et dit: Point de part pour nous avec David, point d\u2019h\u00e9ritage pour nous avec le fils d\u2019Isa\u00ef! Chacun \u00e0 sa tente, Isra\u00ebl!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.2","name":"2 Samuel 20:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.19.43","name":"2 Samuel 19:43","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.19.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Et tous les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl s\u2019\u00e9loign\u00e8rent de David, et suivirent Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri. Mais les hommes de Juda rest\u00e8rent fid\u00e8les \u00e0 leur roi, et l\u2019accompagn\u00e8rent depuis le Jourdain jusqu\u2019\u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.3","name":"2 Samuel 20:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.1","name":"2 Samuel 20:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>David rentra dans sa maison \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Le roi prit les dix concubines qu\u2019il avait laiss\u00e9es pour garder la maison, et il les mit dans un lieu o\u00f9 elles \u00e9taient s\u00e9questr\u00e9es; il pourvut \u00e0 leur entretien, mais il n\u2019alla point vers elles. Et elles furent enferm\u00e9es jusqu\u2019au jour de leur mort, vivant dans un \u00e9tat de veuvage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.4","name":"2 Samuel 20:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.2","name":"2 Samuel 20:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Amasa: Convoque-moi d\u2019ici \u00e0 trois jours les hommes de Juda; et toi, sois ici pr\u00e9sent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.5","name":"2 Samuel 20:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.3","name":"2 Samuel 20:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Amasa partit pour convoquer Juda; mais il tarda au-del\u00e0 du temps que le roi lui avait fix\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.6","name":"2 Samuel 20:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.4","name":"2 Samuel 20:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>David dit alors \u00e0 Abischa\u00ef: Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri, va maintenant nous faire plus de mal qu\u2019Absalom. Prends toi-m\u00eame les serviteurs de ton ma\u00eetre et poursuis-le, de peur qu\u2019il ne trouve des villes fortes et ne se d\u00e9robe \u00e0 nos yeux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.7","name":"2 Samuel 20:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.5","name":"2 Samuel 20:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et Abischa\u00ef partit, suivi des gens de Joab, des K\u00e9r\u00e9thiens et des P\u00e9l\u00e9thiens, et de tous les vaillants hommes; ils sortirent de J\u00e9rusalem, afin de poursuivre Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.8","name":"2 Samuel 20:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.6","name":"2 Samuel 20:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils furent pr\u00e8s de la grande pierre qui est \u00e0 Gabaon, Amasa arriva devant eux. Joab \u00e9tait ceint d\u2019une \u00e9p\u00e9e par-dessus les habits dont il \u00e9tait rev\u00eatu; elle \u00e9tait attach\u00e9e \u00e0 ses reins dans le fourreau, d\u2019o\u00f9 elle glissa, comme Joab s\u2019avan\u00e7ait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.9","name":"2 Samuel 20:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.7","name":"2 Samuel 20:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Joab dit \u00e0 Amasa: Te portes-tu bien, mon fr\u00e8re? Et de la main droite il saisit la barbe d\u2019Amasa pour le baiser.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.10","name":"2 Samuel 20:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.8","name":"2 Samuel 20:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Amasa ne prit point garde \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e qui \u00e9tait dans la main de Joab; et Joab l\u2019en frappa au ventre et r\u00e9pandit ses entrailles \u00e0 terre, sans lui porter un second coup. Et Amasa mourut. Joab et son fr\u00e8re Abischa\u00ef march\u00e8rent \u00e0 la poursuite de Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.11","name":"2 Samuel 20:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.9","name":"2 Samuel 20:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Un homme d\u2019entre les gens de Joab resta pr\u00e8s d\u2019Amasa, et il disait: Qui veut de Joab et qui est pour David? Qu\u2019il suive Joab!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.12","name":"2 Samuel 20:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.10","name":"2 Samuel 20:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Amasa se roulait dans le sang au milieu de la route; et cet homme, ayant vu que tout le peuple s\u2019arr\u00eatait, poussa Amasa hors de la route dans un champ, et jeta sur lui un v\u00eatement, lorsqu\u2019il vit que tous ceux qui arrivaient pr\u00e8s de lui s\u2019arr\u00eataient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.13","name":"2 Samuel 20:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.11","name":"2 Samuel 20:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Quand il fut \u00f4t\u00e9 de la route, chacun suivit Joab, afin de poursuivre Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.14","name":"2 Samuel 20:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.12","name":"2 Samuel 20:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Mort de Sch\u00e9ba<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-22: cf. Ec 9:13-18. Ps 140.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Joab traversa toutes les tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dans la direction d\u2019Abel-Beth-Maaca, et tous les hommes d\u2019\u00e9lite se rassembl\u00e8rent et le suivirent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.15","name":"2 Samuel 20:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.13","name":"2 Samuel 20:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ils vinrent assi\u00e9ger Sch\u00e9ba dans Abel-Beth-Maaca, et ils \u00e9lev\u00e8rent contre la ville une terrasse qui atteignait le rempart. Tout le peuple qui \u00e9tait avec Joab sapait la muraille pour la faire tomber.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.16","name":"2 Samuel 20:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.14","name":"2 Samuel 20:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Alors une femme habile se mit \u00e0 crier de la ville: \u00c9coutez, \u00e9coutez! Dites, je vous prie, \u00e0 Joab: Approche jusqu\u2019ici, je veux te parler!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.17","name":"2 Samuel 20:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.15","name":"2 Samuel 20:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il s\u2019approcha d\u2019elle, et la femme dit: Es-tu Joab? Il r\u00e9pondit: Je le suis. Et elle lui dit: \u00c9coute les paroles de ta servante. Il r\u00e9pondit: J\u2019\u00e9coute.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.18","name":"2 Samuel 20:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.16","name":"2 Samuel 20:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et elle dit: Autrefois on avait coutume de dire: Que l\u2019on consulte Abel! Et tout se terminait ainsi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.19","name":"2 Samuel 20:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.17","name":"2 Samuel 20:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Je suis une des villes paisibles et fid\u00e8les en Isra\u00ebl; et tu cherches \u00e0 faire p\u00e9rir une ville qui est une m\u00e8re en Isra\u00ebl! Pourquoi d\u00e9truirais-tu l\u2019h\u00e9ritage de l\u2019\u00c9ternel?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.20","name":"2 Samuel 20:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.18","name":"2 Samuel 20:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Joab r\u00e9pondit: Loin, loin de moi la pens\u00e9e de d\u00e9truire et de ruiner!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.21","name":"2 Samuel 20:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.19","name":"2 Samuel 20:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>La chose n\u2019est pas ainsi. Mais un homme de la montagne d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, nomm\u00e9 Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri, a lev\u00e9 la main contre le roi David; livrez-le, lui seul, et je m\u2019\u00e9loignerai de la ville. La femme dit \u00e0 Joab: Voici, sa t\u00eate te sera jet\u00e9e par la muraille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.22","name":"2 Samuel 20:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.20","name":"2 Samuel 20:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Et la femme alla vers tout le peuple avec sa sagesse; et ils coup\u00e8rent la t\u00eate \u00e0 Sch\u00e9ba, fils de Bicri, et la jet\u00e8rent \u00e0 Joab. Joab sonna de la trompette; on se dispersa loin de la ville, et chacun s\u2019en alla dans sa tente. Et Joab retourna \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, vers le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.23","name":"2 Samuel 20:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.21","name":"2 Samuel 20:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.024,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 23-26: cf. 2 S 8:15-18. 1 R 4:1-6. 1 Co 12:28, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>\n    Joab commandait toute l\u2019arm\u00e9e d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; Benaja, fils de Jehojada, \u00e9tait \u00e0 la t\u00eate des K\u00e9r\u00e9thiens et des P\u00e9l\u00e9thiens;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.24","name":"2 Samuel 20:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.22","name":"2 Samuel 20:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.24","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:24","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Adoram \u00e9tait pr\u00e9pos\u00e9 aux imp\u00f4ts; Josaphat, fils d\u2019Achilud, \u00e9tait archiviste;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.25","name":"2 Samuel 20:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.23","name":"2 Samuel 20:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.25","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:25","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.020.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Scheja \u00e9tait secr\u00e9taire; Tsadok et Abiathar \u00e9taient sacrificateurs;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.26","name":"2 Samuel 20:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20.24","name":"2 Samuel 20:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.20.26","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 20:26","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.020.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.021.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.20.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>et Ira de Ja\u00efr \u00e9tait ministre d\u2019\u00e9tat de David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.20","name":"2 Samuel 20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sa